description:
* REAL POSTCARDS AND CHRISTMAS CARDS from your iPhone. A simple and meaningful way to share memories and make people smile! 

* Have fun! Make a collage of photos for the front of your card. 

* Surprise and delight! Touchnote is the easiest way to make somebody feel special, with a personalised card they will keep. 

* All cards include FREE USA & WORLDWIDE POSTAGE. 


Full delivery information. 

Postcards 
==================== 
USA: 2-5 working days 
UK: 1-2 working days 
Germany: 1-2 working days 
Rest of Europe: 3-5 working days 
Australia: 1-4 working days 
Other countries: up to 10 working days 

Postcards cost $1.99-$2.99 depending on the destination, or as little as $1.33 when sending in bulk! 


Greeting cards 
==================== 
USA: 2-5 working days 
UK: 1-2 working days 
Europe: 3-5 working days 
Other countries: up to 10 working days 

Greeting cards cost $3.98-$5.98 depending on the destination, or as little as $2.66 when sending in bulk! 


We’re the most popular and trusted app 
============================= 
We’ve sent over TWO MILLION CARDS and have been featured in iTunes's 'New and Noteworthy', The Daily Mail, Forbes , MS-NBC, The Washington Post, Mashable and more. 


Beautiful cards guaranteed 
==================== 
Our postcards are printed on thick 300gsm 6” x 4” card. 
Our greeting cards are printed on heavy 5.8" x 4.2" card.
All cards are coated with a gloss laminate.

Each card comes with our MONEY-BACK GUARANTEE. If your card is lost, damaged or not happy for any reason, we’ll resend your card for free or return your money. 


Who will you surprise with a card?
releaseNotes:
Yes, it's that time of year again. 

Touchnote Holiday cards are back, and they're bigger (by about an inch) and better (gloss laminate, bespoke envelopes, beautiful designs) than ever before.

Send this year's Holiday cards without leaving the couch!

With the Touchnote app you can:
- Turn any photo into a beautiful Holiday card with our seasonal designs
- Use festive illustrations alongside your photos to create Holiday collages 
- Send all your Holiday cards in one go - just add lots of addresses to one card and we'll update the message to make each card personalised
- Get 24-hour assistance from our help team (help@touchnote.com), they're always ready to remedy any problems

*Touchnote Holiday cards are printed and posted in the USA.*
